rom time to time by the Landlord, his agent or employee shall not be deemed a waiver of this term.</span></p> <p class="normal" style="line-height:normal">&nbsp;</p> <p class="normal" style="line-height:normal"><b><span style="font-size:9.0pt; ">d. </span></b><span style="font-size:8.0pt;">It is further agreed between the parties that the rent chargeable pursuant to this Agreement and any statutory or other renewals thereof has been negotiated taking into account a reduction to allow for any future disruptions or inconvenience the Tenant may experience due to the Landlord carrying out its statutory obligations under provincial legislation or any other provincial, federal or municipal legislation; in which case the Tenant shall not seek damages or any abatement of rent.</span></p> </div> 	None	8
